<b>4 sec\/speed 7<b><\/strong>. Transfer to a bowl and set aside."},{"content":"Place olive oil, garlic clove and shallots in mixing bowl and chop <b>5 sec\/speed 5<b>, then sauté <b>3 min\/120°C\/speed 1<b>."},{"content":"Add courgettes and chop <b>8 sec\/speed 4<b>, then sauté <b>4 min\/120°C\/speed 1<b>. Transfer to bowl with chopped parsley and set aside."},{"content":"Place water and chicken stock paste in mixing bowl then heat <strong><b>5 min\/100°C\/speed 1<b><\/strong>. Transfer to bowl with couscous, stir with spatula to moisten the couscous, cover with cling film and allow to sit for 10 minutes."},{"content":"Gently break apart and fluff the cooked couscous with a fork. Add reserved chopped parsley-courgette mixture to couscous, mix gently and crumble feta over the courgette couscous. Serve couscous hot with the red pepper chicken."}],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","55m","6 portions"]}